channel.title: How much do you play Rs?
channel.description:
Well I want to know how much you guys play rs. What is it to you? Do you like it, hate it, or is it your life? I also want you guys to fill this out.
App. hours playing Rs/daily: #
My rankings:
0-2 hours: Just hanging 2-5 hours: like playing it 5-8 hours: um...addicted? 8-10 hours: Primary standing 10-??? hours:(You are 1 or more of the following) OMFG YOUR A RS NERD. IT IS YOUR LIFE, YOUR ADDICTED AND NEED HELP! QUIT WHILE YOU STILL CAN!
Edit: i fixed the daily word because if you guys played 2 hours a day you would be playing about 14 hours a week.

item.title: How much do you play Rs?
item.dc:creator: @x0_0wn x0 0wn
item.description:
@x0_0wn wrote:

Ok you have it ALL wrong.

This is what it should be

0 - 3 Hours: Not much
4-8 Hours: Enjoy playing a bit
9-12 Hours: Like Playing the game
13-15 Hours: Like playing alot
15+ Hours: Love the game.

If you play 1 hour a day that equals 7 hours, how can that mean you’re addicted ?

People can play 3 - 5 hours a day, I know people who do 10
That’s 70 hours.
That would be addicted.

4 hours a day max would be good.
Personally I do about 13 - 15 hours.
